OL,3,CPensioner left depressed and nervous
OL,4,Cafter rogue roofers con him of money
OL,6,FThe victim of a team of rogue roofers
OL,7,Fwho conned him and others out of more
OL,8,Fthan #176,000 says the crimes have
OL,9,Fleft him feeling depressed and nervous.
OL,11,FRon Linton, 79, was contacted by
OL,12,Fworkmen from a Preston-based company
OL,13,FDrySky Property Maintenance after
OL,14,Frequesting work on his garage roof
OL,15,Fonline.
