OL,3,CPensioner left depressed and nervous
OL,4,Cafter rogue roofers con him of money
OL,6,FWhen one of the men, Steve Lee Junior,
OL,7,Fturned up to assess the property he
OL,8,Fspotted more work which needed doing
OL,9,Fon house roof - quoting #11,300 to fix
OL,10,Fboth and telling him the work was
OL,11,Fnecessary.
OL,13,FMr Linton was then intimidated into
OL,14,Fpaying #9,000 of the money upfront for
OL,15,Fthe over-priced work.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
