OL,3,CPensioner left depressed and nervous
OL,4,Cafter rogue roofers con him of money
OL,6,FDrySky Property Maintenance failed to
OL,7,Fcarry out many of the repairs and, two
OL,8,Fweeks into the job, Lee Junior's
OL,9,Ffather - who was also known as Steven
OL,10,F- demanded Ron pay the rest of the
OL,11,Fbalance.
OL,13,F"The experience with them," Mr Linton
OL,14,Fsaid, "it left me very depressed and a
OL,15,Flittle bit nervous.
OL,17,F"I'm not a millionaire, I'm a
OL,18,Fpensioner, it's quite a significant
OL,19,Fsum for me to lose."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
