OL,3,CPensioner left depressed and nervous
OL,4,Cafter rogue roofers con him of money
OL,6,FHe added: "There they were using
OL,7,Fthreatening behaviour, they got my
OL,8,Froof in pieces otherwise the ceiling
OL,9,Fwould be coming through.
OL,11,F"As it turns out the work they
OL,12,Factually did was only a fraction of
OL,13,Fwhat needed to be done, and then they
OL,14,Fabandoned it anyway."
OL,16,FMr Linton was one of eight homeowners
OL,17,Facross the North West targeted by trio
OL,18,FSteven Lee Senior, his son Steven Lee
OL,19,FJunior and Eli Young.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
