OL,3,CPensioner left depressed and nervous
OL,4,Cafter rogue roofers con him of money
OL,6,FThey used aggression, intimidation and
OL,7,Finflated prices to carry out
OL,8,Funnecessary work on roofs that were
OL,9,Fleft in an exposed and dangerous state.
OL,11,FThe trio found Mr Linton after he
OL,12,Fadvertised the work to replace the
OL,13,Fgarage roof on a trading website,
OL,14,Fcontacting him just a few hours later.
OL,16,FA day later Lee Junior arrived to
OL,17,Finspect the job which needed to be
OL,18,Fdone.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
