OL,3,CPensioner left depressed and nervous
OL,4,Cafter rogue roofers con him of money
OL,6,F"I got a phone call from this Steven
OL,7,FLee Junior, he came round, looked at
OL,8,Fthe situation, he said 'oh yes, that's
OL,9,Fno problem'," Mr Linton said.
OL,11,F"He looked at the state of the garage
OL,12,Froof, which had asbestos panels on
OL,13,Fwhich were broken, and the skylights
OL,14,Fwhich were broken and said 'oh yes, we
OL,15,Fcan do that, new steel panels, new
OL,16,Flighting in them and some cosmetic
OL,17,Fstrips around the side' and quoted a
OL,18,Fprice of about #2,700.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
