OL,3,CPensioner left depressed and nervous
OL,4,Cafter rogue roofers con him of money
OL,6,F"Which was a lot of money to me and
OL,7,Fthe job needed to be doing and he was
OL,8,Fthe only person who actually
OL,9,Fresponded."
OL,11,FHe added: "He came back later and said
OL,12,F'oh there's a few lose tiles there', I
OL,13,Fwas aware of those and he said 'we can
OL,14,Fdo some repair work on that'.
OL,16,F"I was aware one small leak in the
OL,17,Froof near the skylights so I invited
OL,18,Fhim to come up and have a look around
OL,19,Fand they then quoted what ended up as
OL,20,Fa total bill for the two properties as
OL,21,Fsomething like #11,500."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
