OL,3,CPensioner left depressed and nervous
OL,4,Cafter rogue roofers con him of money
OL,6,FThe cowboys were eventually caught
OL,7,Fafter a multi-agency investigation
OL,8,Finvolving Stockport Council.
OL,10,FLee Senior pleaded guilty to running a
OL,11,Ffraudulent business, although he died
OL,12,Fbefore he could be sentenced.
OL,14,FLee Junior pleaded guilty to eight
OL,15,Foffences of fraud by false
OL,16,Frepresentation, which also includes
OL,17,Fwork carried out - under different
OL,18,Fcompany names - along with business
OL,19,Fassociate Young.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
