OL,3,CPensioner left depressed and nervous
OL,4,Cafter rogue roofers con him of money
OL,6,FYoung has pleaded guilty to false
OL,7,Frepresentation for his involvement in
OL,8,Fthe roofing business.
OL,10,FBoth will be sentenced in October.
OL,12,FMr Linton's roof was finally sorted
OL,13,Fafter another firm put things right
OL,14,Ffor a fraction of the price, just
OL,15,F#3,500.
OL,17,F"When we got up there is wasn't in the
OL,18,Fbest state really," Rick Gaffey, from
OL,19,FD&G Roofing Joinery, said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
