OL,6,FPartner Paul Davies added: "There was
OL,7,Fholes in the roof where, instead of
OL,8,Fripping the slate our with a slate rip
OL,9,Fthey just smashed holes in the roof to
OL,10,Fget the slates out.
OL,12,F"Basically left him with a roof where
OL,13,Fif it rained there was a lot of water
OL,14,Fand it was leaking."
OL,16,FMark Glynn, Director for Place
OL,17,FManagement at Stockport Council, said:
OL,18,F"I would like to extend my sincere
OL,19,Fthanks to the witnesses who helped
OL,20,Fbring this case to court.
